update CTL_INPUT_FILES_LOADING set status_cd='OUT' where file_id=#GLOBAL.V_MCRM_OUT_FILE_ID

select substr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', 1, instr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', '\', -1, 1)) ||'arc\' ||substr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', instr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', '\', -1, 1)+1, instr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT','.',-1) - (instr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', '\', -1, 1)+1) ) ||'_'||'#GLOBAL.V_CRM_OUT_FILE_ID' ||'_'||'#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_LOAD_DT' ||substr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', instr('#GLOBAL.V_CRM_FILE_NAME_2_OUT', '.',-1)) from dual

select nvl(max(file_id), -1) from ( select file_id from CTL_INPUT_FILES_LOADING where status_cd='DWH' and SOURCE_NAME in ('CRM') and rownum<=1 union all select null from dual )
